- Custom Filters : Add your own websites and keywords by URL to block them
- Security Filters : App updated with more security filters for you to enable from. Protect yourself from all those internet scams and frauds
- Adult Content Blocker : Enabling this feature will turn your phone into child protection mode. This feature will keep your children away from viewing or even opening these websites
- Privacy Protection : We have stepped up our game with adding 100k+ advertising domains that protects your surfing from these ads. Blocks all privacy related content including tracking and sending third party information
- General Bug Fixes and Stability Improvements
